Frequently Asked Questions



Welcome to our Sneakify website's FAQ page! Below are answers to common questions about our products, services, and policies. If you need further assistance, please feel free to contact our customer support team.

1. What types of shoes do you offer?

We offer a diverse range of sneakers for men, women, and kids. Our collection includes athletic sneakers, lifestyle sneakers, and footwear designed for comfort and support for the whole family.

2. Are your sneakers authentic?

Yes, we guarantee that all of our products are 100% authentic. We source our sneakers directly from reputable manufacturers and authorized distributors.

3. How do I determine my shoe size?

To find your perfect fit, we recommend using our size chart, which you can find on each product page. Measure your foot length and width and compare it to the measurements provided to select the right size for you or your family members.

4. What is your return policy?

We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you're not happy with your sneakers or keto shoes, Products are returnable within the applicable return window(7 days) if you've received them in a condition that is physically damaged, has missing parts or accessories, defective or different from their description on the product detail page on Sneakify Website. Please ensure the shoes are unworn and in their original condition with the tags attached.

5. Are your shoes made from sustainable materials?

We're committed to sustainability, and many of our shoes are made from eco-friendly materials such as recycled plastics, organic cotton, and sustainable leather alternatives.

6. Do you offer international shipping?

No,we don't offer international shipping to many countries worldwide.we only ship our shoes to our country only. Shipping costs and delivery times may vary depending on your location.

7. How do I care for my sneakers?

To keep your sneakers looking their best, we recommend cleaning them regularly with a mild detergent and a soft brush. Avoid exposing them to harsh chemicals or extreme temperatures.

8. Can I cancel or modify my order?

We process orders quickly to ensure prompt delivery, but if you need to cancel or modify your order, You can choose to cancel an order any time before it's dispatched. The order cannot be canceled once it’s out for delivery. However, the customer may choose to reject it at the doorstep. The time window for cancellation varies based on different categories and the order cannot be canceled once the specified time has passed.

9. Are your sneakers suitable for athletic activities?

While many of our sneakers are designed with comfort and durability in mind, their suitability for specific athletic activities may vary. We recommend checking the product descriptions for any features tailored to sports performance, such as cushioning, support, and traction.

10. What should I do if my sneakers arrive damaged or defective?

If you receive damaged or defective sneakers, please contact our customer service team immediately with photos of the issue. We will work quickly to resolve the problem and provide you with a replacement or refund as necessary.

11. What payment methods do you accept?

We accept various payment methods, including credit/debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express, RuPay) and other secure online payment platforms.

12. Do you accept cash on delivery?

For customers who prefer to pay in cash, we offer a Cash on Delivery (COD) option. With COD, you can pay for your order at the time of delivery. Please note that COD orders may be subject to additional verification to ensure the security of transactions.

13. Do you offer customization or personalization options for sneakers?

At this time, we do not offer customization or personalization services for sneakers. However, we regularly update our inventory with a wide variety of styles and colors to suit different tastes.

14. What kind of security measures are taken for kids?

Sneakify does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child under the age of 13, we will take steps to delete it immediately.

15. How do I find the product I'm looking for on the website?

You can find our products on our website through a simple search. Enter the product name in the search option on the top of the page. After completing the search, you can add the selected products you want by clicking on the option ‘Add to wishlist.'

16. How can I solve my queries?

If you have any questions or need assistance, you can reach our customer support team through our contact form on the website. We're here to help you with any concerns or inquiries you may have.

We hope this FAQ page has been helpful! If you have any further questions or feedback, don't hesitate to get in touch with us. Thank you for choosing our shoe website for your family's footwear needs!
